title: WOMEN ULTRA LIGHT DOWN JACKET
detail:
Ultra Light Down: now even comfier.

Durable water-repellent coating.
Pocketable design can be stored in the carrying pouch.
In response to customer feedback, we've updated the chest width for greater comfort.
Soft stretch tape added inside the sleeves keep them in place when rolled up.
Seam is aligned with stitches behind waist to maintain a streamlined silhouette.
Contoured round collar with new stitch-free tag.
Double elastic on the hem for a snug fit.
More relaxed fit for easy movement.
Matte finish looks great whether you're playing sports or just hanging out.
Carrying pouch attaches to inside loop on the left.
materials:
[03 Gray] Shell: 65% Nylon, 35% Polyester/ Filling: Down(minimum90% Down) Lining: 100% Polyester [Other Color] Shell: 100% Nylon/ Filling: Down (Minimum 90% Down) Lining: 100% Nylon
Hand wash cold
Imported

title: WOMEN ULTRA LIGHT DOWN COMPACT JACKET
detail:
Easy-to-layer two-way jacket. Updated based on customer feedback.

Newly updated with a lining that reduces static.
Durable water-repellent coating.
Pocketable design can be stored in the carrying pouch.
Easy-to-coordinate matte finish.
Soft stretch tape added inside the sleeves to keep them in place when rolled up.
Collar can also be worn as a V neck under a coat.
Improved V-neck design.
Carrying pouch attaches to inside loop on the left.
